lead_paragraph: The pass-happy Golden State Warriors put on a spectacular offensive show for their former coach, and Luke Walton had to watch the onslaught against his Los Angeles Lakers from the other bench this time.

headline.print_headline: Curry, Pass-Happy Warriors Rout Lakers This Time, 149-106
